{{Joe Biden series}}
'''2021年美國總統就職典禮'''，正式名稱為'''第59屆美國總統就職典禮'''（{{lang-en|59th Presidential Inaugural Ceremonies}}），又稱'''喬·拜登總統就職典禮'''（{{lang-en|Inauguration of Joe Biden}}），是与2021年1月20日星期三在[[华盛顿哥伦比亚特区|華盛頓特區]][[美國國會大廈|美國國會大廈]]西翼举行的[[美国总统就职典礼|就职典礼]]，標誌著第46任[[美国总统|美国总统]][[乔·拜登|乔·拜登]]及第49任[[美国副总统|副總統]][[賀錦麗|賀錦麗]]將在這天正式就任並進行宣誓，标志两人正式开始四年執政期。

就职典礼时值美国政治、公共卫生、经济及国家安全形势空前严峻之时：即將卸任的[[美国总统|美国总统]][[唐纳德·特朗普|唐纳德·特朗普]]曾一度{{Internal link helper/en|试图推翻2020年美国总统选举结果|Attempts to overturn the 2020 United States presidential election|尝试推翻}}[[2020年美国总统选举|2020年美国总统选举]]结果，促使特朗普的支持者于1月6日[[2021年冲击美国国会大厦事件|冲击国会大厦]]，使特朗普被控[[煽动叛乱|煽动叛乱]]而面临史无前例的[[第二次特朗普弹劾案|第二次弹劾案]]，加上全国各地面临{{le|2021年美国国会抗议活动|2021 United States capitol protests|大规模骚乱}}的威胁，执法部门大为紧张。又因为[[2019冠状病毒病疫情|2019冠状病毒病疫情]]的影响，加上安保的需要，典礼活动被大幅度限缩，避免[[2019冠状病毒病|病毒]]进一步扩散，也减少国会周边地区爆发暴力活动的可能性<ref>{{Cite news|authors=Lisa Mascaro & Mary Clare Jalonick|title=Trump impeachment trial to focus on his attacks on election|url=https://apnews.com/article/trump-impeached-after-capitol-riot-cd210a7c362966f6c93bdf1a1cf1b190|agency=Associated Press|date=2021-01-14|accessdate=2021-01-18|archive-date=2021-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116230315/https://apnews.com/article/trump-impeached-after-capitol-riot-cd210a7c362966f6c93bdf1a1cf1b190|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|authors=Felicia Sonmez, Colby Itkowitz, John Wagner, Paulina Firozi & Nick Miroff|title=Acting homeland security secretary Wolf to step down, nine days ahead of Biden inauguration|newspaper=Washington Post|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/2021/01/11/trump-impeachment-biden-transition-live-updates/|date=2021-01-11|accessdate=2021-01-18|archive-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118214439/https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/2021/01/11/trump-impeachment-biden-transition-live-updates/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，故是次典礼仅开放[[第117届美国国会|第117届美国国会]]成员现场观礼，他们仅可以选择携带一名嘉宾前往，做法和[[国情咨文|国情咨文]]演说类似<ref name="Inaugural-Attendance2">{{Cite web|last=|first=|date=2020-12-16|title=JCCIC Announces Attendance Guidelines for 59th Inaugural Ceremonies|url=https://www.inaugural.senate.gov/press_release/jccic-announces-attendance-guidelines-for-59th-inaugural-ceremonies/|dead-url=no|publisher=Joint Congressional Committee on Inaugural Ceremonies|accessdate=2021-01-18|archive-date=2020-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201219082030/https://www.inaugural.senate.gov/press_release/jccic-announces-attendance-guidelines-for-59th-inaugural-ceremonies/}}</ref>。观礼人士必须接受核酸检测及测温，并全程佩戴口罩及[[保持社交距离|保持社交距离]]<ref name=":02">{{Cite news|last1=Shear|first1=Michael D.|last2=Fandos|first2=Nicholas|date=2020-11-30|title=Biden's Inauguration: Expect Smaller Crowds and More Social Distancing|newspaper=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/30/us/politics/biden-inauguration.html|dead-url=no|access-date=2021-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114194202/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/30/us/politics/biden-inauguration.html|archive-date=2021-01-14}}</ref>。

此次典礼主题“美国團結”（America United）、“我们坚定的民主：锻造更美好的合众国”（Our Determined Democracy: Forging a More Perfect Union）参考自[[美国宪法序言|美国宪法序言]]<ref name="2020-11-02 Hill">{{cite news|last=Blunt|first=Roy|date=2020-11-02|title=59th inaugural ceremonies: 'Our Determined Democracy: Forging a More Perfect Union'|work=The Hill|url=https://thehill.com/blogs/congress-blog/politics/524050-59th-inaugural-ceremonies-our-determined-democracy-forging-a|dead-url=no|access-date=2021-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201228040449/https://thehill.com/blogs/congress-blog/politics/524050-59th-inaugural-ceremonies-our-determined-democracy-forging-a|archive-date=2020-12-28}}</ref>。

==背景==
{{Main|乔·拜登的总统过渡}}
就职典礼标志着在[[2020年美国总统选举|2020年美国总统选举]]中[[美国总统当选人|当选]]的[[乔·拜登|乔·拜登]]正式结束总统过渡期<ref>{{cite news|url=https://apnews.com/article/Biden-Trump-US-election-2020-results-fd58df73aa677acb74fce2a69adb71f9|title=Biden wins White House, vowing new direction for divided US|first1=Jonathan|last1=Lemire|first2=Zeke|last2=Miller|date=2020-11-07|agency=Associated Press|access-date=2020-01-13|archive-date=2020-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107195759/https://apnews.com/article/Biden-Trump-US-election-2020-results-fd58df73aa677acb74fce2a69adb71f9|dead-url=no}}</ref>。拜登与竞选搭档[[贺锦丽|贺锦丽]]于2020年12月14日的[[选举人团_(美国)|选举人团]]投票中，被正式确认胜出大选<ref name="ElectoralCollege">{{cite news|last1=Parks|first1=Miles|title=Electoral College Affirms Biden Victory As Trump Continues Baseless Challenges|url=https://www.npr.org/sections/biden-transition-updates/2020/12/14/946365392/electoral-college-affirms-biden-victory-as-trump-continues-baseless-challenges|publisher=NPR|date=2020-12-14|access-date=2020-12-14|archive-date=2021-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114194210/https://www.npr.org/sections/biden-transition-updates/2020/12/14/946365392/electoral-college-affirms-biden-victory-as-trump-continues-baseless-challenges|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而，不断质疑选举合法性，但在落败整整两个月后承诺“有序交接”权力的[[唐纳德·特朗普|唐纳德·特朗普]]不打算出席典礼，成为自1869年时任总统[[安德鲁·约翰逊|安德鲁·约翰逊]]拒绝出席[[尤利西斯·格兰特|尤利西斯·格兰特]]{{tsl|en|first inauguration of Ulysses S. Grant|尤利西斯·格兰特第一次就职典礼|第一次就职典礼}}以来，首位这样做的现任总统，是美国史上第四位这样做的现任总统<ref name="Ceremony">{{cite news|last=Balcerski|first=Thomas|date=2020-11-11|title=A history lesson on presidents who snub their successors' inaugurations|url=https://www.cnn.com/2020/11/11/opinions/presidents-history-skipping-inauguration-day-balcerski/index.html|access-date=2020-12-02|publisher=CNN|archive-date=2021-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114194221/https://www.cnn.com/2020/11/11/opinions/presidents-history-skipping-inauguration-day-balcerski/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Transition">{{cite news|last=Malloy|first=Ally|date=2020-01-07|title=Trump pledges orderly transition after Congress affirms Biden's win and Capitol riot|url=https://www.cnn.com/2021/01/07/politics/trump-biden-us-capitol-electoral-college-insurrection/index.html|access-date=2021-01-07|work=CNN|archive-date=2021-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107095401/https://www.cnn.com/2021/01/07/politics/trump-biden-us-capitol-electoral-college-insurrection/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

一就职，拜登会凭78岁又61天的高龄，成为[[美国总统上任时年龄列表|上任时最年长的美国总统]]，打败卸任时77岁又349天的[[罗纳德·里根|罗纳德·里根]]的纪录。他还会是首位[[特拉华州|特拉华州]]籍的总统、[[约翰·肯尼迪|约翰·肯尼迪]]后第二位{{tsl|en|Religious affiliations of presidents of the United States|美国总统宗教信仰|天主教信徒}}总统、第十五位担任总统的前副总统<ref>{{cite news|last1=Cormier|first1=Ryan|last2=Talorico|first2=Patricia|title=Delaware history is made: The First State gets its first president in Joe Biden|url=https://www.delawareonline.com/story/news/politics/2020/11/07/one-us-delaware-pride-soars-biden-makes-history/6121243002/|access-date=2020-11-08|work=Delaware Online|date=2020-11-07|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108021346/https://www.delawareonline.com/story/news/politics/2020/11/07/one-us-delaware-pride-soars-biden-makes-history/6121243002/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2020/11/05/oldest-president-joe-biden/6181672002/|title=Joe Biden will become the oldest president in American history, a title previously held by Ronald Reagan|first=Josh|last=Peter|date=2020-11-07|work=USA Today|access-date=2020-01-13|archive-date=2020-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107182039/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2020/11/05/oldest-president-joe-biden/6181672002/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。贺锦丽将成为首位[[亚裔美国人|亚]][[非裔美国人|非裔]]女副总统<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/08/11/us/politics/kamala-harris-vp-biden.html|title=Kamala Harris Is Biden's Choice for Vice President|first1=Alexander|last1=Burns|first2=Katie|last2=Glueck|date=2020-08-17|work=The New York Times|access-date=2020-11-06|archive-date=2020-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107195845/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/08/11/us/politics/kamala-harris-vp-biden.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==组织者==
===国会联席委员会===
当选总统拜登及当选副总统贺锦丽的宣誓仪式由[[美國國會就職典禮聯席委員會|就职典礼联席委员会]]筹划。联席委员会由两党人士组成，包括[[美国参议院|参议员]][[罗伊·布伦特|罗伊·布伦特]]（任主席）、[[米奇·麥康諾|米奇·麥康諾]]、[[艾米·克罗布彻|艾米·克罗布彻]]和[[美国众议院|众议员]][[南希·佩洛西|南希·佩洛西]]、[[斯坦利·霍耶|斯坦利·霍耶]]和[[凱文·麥卡錫_(加利福尼亞州政治家)|凯文·麦卡锡]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.inaugural.senate.gov/about-the-committee|title=Membership of the Joint Congressional Committee on Inaugural Ceremonies|access-date=2020-11-08|publisher=United States Senate|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109053550/https://www.inaugural.senate.gov/about-the-committee/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="2020-11-02 Hill"/>。{{tsl|en|United States Senate Committee on Rules and Administration|美国参议院规则与行政委员会}}负责监督联席委员会运作<ref name="2020-11-02 Hill"/>。

2020年12月8日，委员会的共和党成员投票反对公开认可拜登和贺锦丽当选的决议<ref>{{cite news |url=https://thehill.com/homenews/house/529276-inauguration-committee-republicans-sink-democrats-resolution-acknowledging |title=Inauguration committee Republicans sink Democrats' resolution acknowledging Biden victory |first=Mike |last=Lillis |date=2020-12-08 |work=The Hill |access-date=2020-12-08 |archive-date=2021-01-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114194209/https://thehill.com/homenews/house/529276-inauguration-committee-republicans-sink-democrats-resolution-acknowledging |dead-url=no }}</ref>。选举人团确认拜登当选后，布伦特及其他{{tsl|en|Senate Republican Conference|参议院共和党人会议|共和党参议员}}最终确认拜登当选总统，表示将与拜登的总统就职委员会就典礼准备事宜进行沟通<ref>{{cite news |url=https://thehill.com/homenews/senate/530194-top-gop-senators-acknowledge-biden-as-president-elect-after-electoral-college |title=Top GOP senators acknowledge Biden as president-elect after Electoral College vote |first=Jordain |last=Carney |date=2020-12-14 |work=The Hill |access-date=2020-12-15 |archive-date=2021-01-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114194159/https://thehill.com/homenews/senate/530194-top-gop-senators-acknowledge-biden-as-president-elect-after-electoral-college |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===总统就职委员会===
2021年总统就职委员会会在当选总统和副总统的指导下筹划多场与就职典礼相关的活动。该委员会由联合主席{{tsl|en|Jim Clyburn|吉姆·克莱本}}、[[埃里克·加塞蒂|埃里克·加塞蒂]]、{{tsl|en|Cedric Richmond|塞德里克·里士满}}、{{tsl|en|Lisa Blunt Rochester|丽莎·布伦特·罗彻斯特}}、[[格雷琴·惠特默|格雷琴·惠特默]]，首席执行官托尼·艾伦，执行主任马优·瓦金斯（Maju Varghese），副执行主任{{tsl|en|Yvanna Cancela|伊凡娜·坎卡}}和艾琳·威尔逊（Erin Wilson），首席医疗顾问{{tsl|en|David A. Kessler|戴维·凯斯勒}}及人员和外部事物主任艾德丽安·埃罗德（Adrienne Elrod）组成<ref name=Forgey>{{Cite news|url=https://www.politico.com/news/2020/11/30/biden-harris-form-inaugural-committee-441355|title=Biden, Harris form inaugural committee|first=Quint|last=Forgey|date=2020-11-30|work=Politico|access-date=2021-01-13|archive-date=2020-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201183612/https://www.politico.com/news/2020/11/30/biden-harris-form-inaugural-committee-441355|dead-url=no}}</ref>。委员会雇佣负责{{tsl|en|2020 Democratic National Convention|2020年美国民主党全国大会}}线上节目制作的{{tsl|en|Stephanie Cutter|斯蒂芬妮·库特}}和{{tsl|en|Ricky Kirshner|里奇·科什纳}}，以及{{tsl|en|Glenn Weiss|格伦·魏斯}}规划典礼的节目转播<ref>{{Cite web|date=2021-01-15|title=Presidential Inaugural Committee Outlines Initial Plans to Honor American Traditions and Protect Public Health {{!}} inauguration|url=https://inauguration.dc.gov/release/presidential-inaugural-committee-outlines-initial-plans-honor-american-traditions-and|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109235007/https://inauguration.dc.gov/release/presidential-inaugural-committee-outlines-initial-plans-honor-american-traditions-and|archive-date=2021-01-09|access-date=2021-01-15|website=inauguration.dc.gov}}</ref>。

==主题和节目==
就职典礼联席委员会选定“我们坚定的民主：锻造更美好的合众国”作为是次就职典礼的主题，凸显典礼是“美国治理与民主的标志”，强调[[政黨輪替|权力平稳交接]]<ref name="2020-11-02 Hill"/>。

拜登就职委员会首席执行官艾伦表示，活动在疫情的影响下会有所不同，但会让美国人在安全的条件下，参与到就职典礼的传统中<ref name=Forgey/>。活动包括由名人主持、为期5天的多场[[网络直播|网络直播]]的音乐会<ref name=":6">{{Cite web|last=Tapp|first=Tom|date=2021-01-15|title=Star-Studded Biden/Harris Inaugural Events To Stretch Over 5 Days, Celebrate "America United"|url=https://deadline.com/2021/01/star-studded-biden-harris-inaugural-events-5-days-celebrate-america-united-1234674481/|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116200332/https://deadline.com/2021/01/star-studded-biden-harris-inaugural-events-5-days-celebrate-america-united-1234674481/|archive-date=2021-01-16|access-date=2021-01-15|website=Deadline}}</ref>。就职典礼的官方[[YouTube|YouTube]]频道及其他[[社交媒体|社交媒体]]账号将发布与典礼相关的独家内容<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.cnn.com/2021/01/11/politics/inauguration-day-theme-america-united/index.html|title='America United' announced as inaugural theme|first=Sarah|last=Mucha|date=2021-01-11|work=CNN|access-date=2021-01-11|archive-date=2021-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114194200/https://www.cnn.com/2021/01/11/politics/inauguration-day-theme-america-united/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

