mporary-shutdown-capitol-evacuation-inaguration-rehearsal-participants-n1254585|dead-url=yes|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125000144/https://www.nbcnews.com/politics/congress/small-fire-prompts-temporary-shutdown-capitol-evacuation-inaguration-rehearsal-participants-n1254585|archive-date=2021-01-25|access-date=2021-01-18|website=NBC News|11=}}</ref>。扮演就职典礼观众的军乐团和其他人士被迫撤离典礼平台<ref name=":16">{{Cite web|last=|first=|date=2021-01-18|title=Inauguration Rehearsal Evacuated, Capitol Shut Down After Fire in DC Homeless Camp|url=https://www.nbcwashington.com/news/local/us-capitol-police-issue-security-warning/2544924/|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118162509/https://www.nbcwashington.com/news/local/us-capitol-police-issue-security-warning/2544924/|archive-date=2021-01-18|access-date=2021-01-18|website=NBC4 Washington}}</ref><ref name=":17" />。营地的小火情最终被迅速扑灭，无人受伤<ref>Karl de Vries, [https://www.cnn.com/2021/01/18/politics/capitol-lockdown-fire/index.html Capitol Building put on alert after a small fire several blocks away] {{Wayback|url=https://www.cnn.com/2021/01/18/politics/capitol-lockdown-fire/index.html |date=20210118172616 }}, January 18, 2021 (CNN).</ref>。火苗烟雾可在国会上空看到<ref name=":15" /><ref name=":17" /><ref name=":18" />。

==典礼前活动==
=== “合众美国”就职典礼欢迎活动 ===
就职典礼的首场活动是于星期六举行的“合众美国：庆祝美国变革者就职典礼欢迎活动”（''America United: An Inauguration Welcome Event Celebrating America’s Changemakers''），将设有一系列音乐表演和政治演讲，庆祝拜登和贺锦丽当选<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|last=Beresford|first=Trilby|date=2021-01-16|title='Victory' of Kamala Harris Celebrated in 'America United: An Inauguration Welcome'|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/9512598/kamala-harris-america-united-an-inauguration-welcome-recap|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117030858/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/9512598/kamala-harris-america-united-an-inauguration-welcome-recap/|archive-date=2021-01-17|access-date=2021-01-16|website=Billboard}}</ref><ref name=":62">{{Cite web|last=Tapp|first=Tom|date=2021-01-15|title=Star-Studded Biden/Harris Inaugural Events To Stretch Over 5 Days, Celebrate "America United"|url=https://deadline.com/2021/01/star-studded-biden-harris-inaugural-events-5-days-celebrate-america-united-1234674481/|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116200332/https://deadline.com/2021/01/star-studded-biden-harris-inaugural-events-5-days-celebrate-america-united-1234674481/|archive-date=2021-01-16|access-date=2021-01-15|website=Deadline-US}}</ref>。网络直播则由女性和[[非二元性别|非二元性别]][[抗议歌曲|抗议歌手]]组成的抵抗复兴合唱团（Resistance Revival Choir）与担任主唱的灵魂歌手{{tsl|en|Deva Mahal|德瓦·玛哈}}共同表演的《Everybody Deserves To Be Free》揭幕。合唱团成员录下各自表演时的影像，直播时会在大屏幕上播放<ref name=":0" />。

随后是[[美国女童军|美国女童军]]率领的[[效忠宣誓|效忠宣誓]]。[[墨西哥裔美国人|美国墨西哥裔]]制片人{{tsl|en|Cristela Alonzo|克里斯黛拉·阿朗索}}会为该节目开场，标志着拜登的就职典礼会为美国历史翻开新一页<ref name=":0" />。新墨西哥州众议院[[德布·哈兰德|德布·哈兰德]]之后叙述[[美洲原住民|美洲原住民]]所做的贡献和斗争，介绍[[奎查恩人|奎查恩]]印第安部落民族领袖克劳代特·怀特（Claudette White）演唱的传统歌曲<ref name=":0" />。表演过后，多位女性政治领袖会远程探讨贺锦丽当选美国首位女副总统带来的影响<ref name=":0" />。阿朗索之后介绍演员{{tsl|en|Nik Dodani|尼克·杜达尼}}和民权社运领袖{{tsl|en|Janet Murguía|珍妮特·穆吉亚}}，前者会发言提到拜登就职的意义，后者会提供{{tsl|en|women of color|有色人种女性}}在2020年总统选举中所获的政治成就<ref name=":0" />。海内外及地方工会领袖，包括[[美国教师联盟|美国教师联盟]]总统{{tsl|en|Randi Weingarten|兰迪·温加顿}}、[[全國教育協會_(美國)|全国教育协会]]主席{{tsl|en|Rebecca S. Pringle|丽贝卡·普林格}}，[[国际消防员协会|消防]]、{{tsl|en|American Federation of Government Employees|美国政府雇佣联合会|政府}}和{{tsl|en|Service Employees International Union|服务业雇佣国际公会|服务}}行业的领袖，[[美国钢铁工人联合会|钢铁]]、{{tsl|en|United Auto Workers|美国汽车工人联合会|汽车}}、{{tsl|en|American Postal Workers Union|美国邮政工人联合会|邮政}}、{{tsl|en|United Food and Commercial Workers|美国食品商业工人联合会|食品}}和{{tsl|en|Communications Workers of America|美国通讯工人联合会|通讯}}行业的工人将祝贺拜登胜选，说他支持他们各自的利益（如{{tsl|en|Fight for $15|争取15美金}}），是他们所在行业工人的成功<ref name=":0" />。

演员[[琥碧·戈柏|琥碧·戈柏]]随后登场，表示她对拜登和贺锦丽所领导的国家感到“乐观”，艺人[[達倫·克里斯|達倫·克里斯]]之后翻唱歌曲《{{tsl|en|(Your Love Keeps Lifting Me) Higher and Higher|(Your Love Keeps Lifting Me) Higher and Higher}}》<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":12">{{Cite web|last=Kreps|first=Daniel|last2=|first2=|date=2021-01-17|title=See Black Pumas Perform 'Colors' for Biden-Harris Inauguration Welcome Event|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/black-pumas-colors-biden-harris-inauguration-welcome-event-1115719/|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117220419/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/black-pumas-colors-biden-harris-inauguration-welcome-event-1115719/|archive-date=2021-01-17|access-date=2021-01-18|website=Rolling Stone-US}}</ref>。拜登竞选团队最大捐款人、[[乔治亚州|乔治亚州]][[亚特兰大|亚特兰大]]市长{{tsl|en|Keisha Lance Bottoms|凯莎·兰斯·巴托姆斯}}随后登场，赞扬拜登“会确保全体美国人的声音都能被听到”<ref name=":0" />。音乐团体{{tsl|en|Black Pumas|Black Pumas}}表演歌曲《Colors》，表示他们希望全体美国人都能保持“一种乐观、团结与和平的感觉”<ref name=":12" />。活动的最后，纽约州众议员[[孟昭文|孟昭文]]介绍贺锦丽，指她“支持为女性（尤其是[[非裔美国人|非裔女性]]）创造参与并引领政坛机会的人士”<ref name=":62" /><ref name=":0" />。

=== 正式歌单 ===
拜登就职委员会发表了[[唱片骑师|唱片骑师]]{{tsl|en|D-Nice|D-Nice}}和音乐厂牌Raedio甄选、{{le|伊萨·雷|Issa Rae}}发表的<ref>{{Cite web|last=Mims|first=Taylor|date=2020-02-13|title=From TV to Music Mogul: How Issa Rae Is Giving Artists A Leg Up|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/business/8550816/issa-rae-productions-raedio-company-insecure-interview|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201122022626/https://www.billboard.com/articles/business/8550816/issa-rae-productions-raedio-company-insecure-interview|archive-date=2020-11-22|access-date=2021-01-18|website=Billboard}}</ref>46首歌曲[[歌单|歌单]]（象征拜登是第46任总统）<ref name=":13">{{Cite web|last=Blistein|first=Jon|last2=|first2=|date=2021-01-15|title=Joe Biden, Kamala Harris Share Inauguration Playlist With Springsteen, Mary J. Blige, and More|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/joe-biden-kamala-harris-inauguration-playlist-springsteen-mary-j-blige-1115096/|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117014022/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/joe-biden-kamala-harris-inauguration-playlist-springsteen-mary-j-blige-1115096/|archive-date=2021-01-17|access-date=2021-01-18|website=Rolling Stone-US}}</ref>。委员会希望歌单能让美国民众借此在家参与就职典礼<ref name=":14">{{Cite web|last=McClearly|first=Kelly|date=2021-01-16|title=Joe Biden and Kamala Harris drop a playlist for your inauguration watch party|url=https://www.cnn.com/2021/01/16/politics/joe-biden-inauguration-playlist/index.html|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117192129/https://www.cnn.com/2021/01/16/politics/joe-biden-inauguration-playlist/index.html|archive-date=2021-01-17|access-date=2021-01-18|website=CNN}}</ref>。歌单在各大主流流媒体平台发布，包括拜登伉俪和贺锦丽伉俪就职典礼当天登场歌曲<ref name=":13" /><ref name=":14" />。据《[[滚石_(杂志)|滚石]]》介绍，拜登的登场曲为[[布魯斯·斯普林斯汀|布魯斯·斯普林斯汀]]的《{{tsl|en|We Take Care of Our Own|We Take Care of Our Own}}》，吉尔·拜登为[[霍爾與奧茲|霍爾與奧茲]]的《{{tsl|en|You Make My Dreams|You Make My Dreams (Come True)}}》，贺锦丽为[[玛丽·布莱姬|玛丽·布莱姬]]的《{{tsl|en|Work That (Mary J. Blige song)|Work That}}》，任德龙为[[激進小子|激進小子]]的《{{tsl|en|You Get What You Give (song)|You Get What You Give}}》<ref name=":13" />。委员会首席执行官艾伦表示入选的音乐“反映美国的不屈不挠的精神和丰富的文化多样性”，作为拜登和贺锦丽开始“团结国家的重要工作”，“为美国历史新一页翻开的配乐”<ref name=":13" /><ref name=":14" />。

=== “我们人民”线上音乐会 ===
就职典礼正式开始前的星期日，拜登就职委员会举行线上筹款音乐会“我们人民”（We the People），由演员[[基根-麥可·奇|基根-麥可·奇]]和[[黛博拉·梅辛|黛博拉·梅辛]]共同主持<ref name=":32">{{Cite web|last=Lejeune|first=Tristan|date=2021-01-14|title=Biden inauguration announces virtual concert 'We the People' on Sunday|url=https://thehill.com/blogs/in-the-know/in-the-know/534276-biden-inauguration-announces-virtual-concert-we-the-people-on|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114192806/https://thehill.com/blogs/in-the-know/in-the-know/534276-biden-inauguration-announces-virtual-concert-we-the-people-on|archive-date=2021-01-14|access-date=2021-01-14|website=TheHill}}</ref>。音乐会现场观众需要向拜登就职委员会才能进入<ref name=":5">{{Cite web|last=Michallon|first=Clémence|date=2021-01-18|title=Cher tells Joe Biden ‘this is your time’ as virtual show kicks off Inauguration Week|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/news/biden-concert-pre-inauguration-live-streaming-b1788692.html|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118030826/https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/news/biden-concert-pre-inauguration-live-streaming-b1788692.html|archive-date=2021-01-18|access-date=2021-01-18|website=The Independent}}</ref>。开场，拜登和妻子吉尔感谢支持自己的选民，承认疫情期间牺牲的生命；拜登表示担任总统是“毕生的荣幸”<ref name=":5" />。

当晚首个表演是{{tsl|en|Ben Harper|本·哈珀}}的歌曲《{{tsl|en|With My Own Two Hands|With My Own Two Hands}}》<ref name=":9">{{Cite web|last=Johnson|first=Ted|last2=|first2=|date=2021-01-18|title=Performers Fete Joe Biden And Kamala Harris At Inauguration Week Kickoff Concert: “This Is Your Time,” Says Cher|url=https://deadline.com/2021/01/performers-fete-joe-biden-and-kamala-harris-at-inaugural-kickoff-concert-this-is-your-time-says-cher-1234675519/|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118052721/https://deadline.com/2021/01/performers-fete-joe-biden-and-kamala-harris-at-inaugural-kickoff-concert-this-is-your-time-says-cher-1234675519/|archive-date=2021-01-18|access-date=2021-01-18|website=Deadline-US}}</ref>。歌手{{tsl|en|Michael Bivins|迈克尔·比文斯}}视频亮相，感谢观众捐款。乐队{{le|AJR乐队|AJR (band)}}演出歌曲《Bummerland》<ref name=":9" />。歌手[[芭芭拉·史翠珊|芭芭拉·史翠珊]]祝贺拜登和贺锦丽上任，期盼他们帮助美国和世界“恢复健康”，并表演美国{{tsl|en|Standard (music)|标准音乐|标准歌曲}}《{{tsl|en|Happy Days Are Here Again|Happy Days Are Here Again}}》<ref name=":9" /><ref name=":5" />。梅辛介绍演员、前{{tsl|en|Presidency of Barack Obama|巴拉克·奥巴马总统任期|巴拉克·奥巴马政府}}职员卡尔·佩恩（Kal Penn），佩恩阐述就职典礼的重要性及对“光明未来”的希望<ref name=":9" />。贺锦丽与丈夫任德龙随后凭视频链接登场，感谢支持者，并列出他们在领导国家时会面临的问题<ref name=":5" />。

说唱歌手[[威廉_(歌手)|威廉]]表演[[公益歌曲|公益歌曲]]《American Dream》<ref name=":9" />，这首歌是威廉的天使基金会（Angel Foundation）将[[理工科|理工科]]教育拓展到[[社会特权|非特权]]学生所推出的筹款歌曲<ref>{{Cite web|last=|first=|date=2021-01-12|title=will.i.am Launches $5 Million “American Dream Fund” for i.am Angel Foundation to Expand Access to STEAM-Focused Education|url=https://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20210112006003/en/will.i.am-Launches-5-Million-%E2%80%9CAmerican-Dream-Fund%E2%80%9D-for-i.am-Angel-Foundation-to-Expand-Access-to-STEAM-Focused-Education|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118053221/https://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20210112006003/en/will.i.am-Launches-5-Million-|archive-date=2021-01-18|access-date=2021-01-18|website=www.businesswire.com}}</ref>。演员、社运人士[[蘇菲亞·布希|蘇菲亞·布希]]感谢向就职委员会捐款的人士，音乐人[[卡洛尔·金|卡洛尔·金]]表演[[格莱美奖年度制作|格莱美奖年度制作]]获奖歌曲《{{tsl|en|You've Got a Friend|You’ve Got a Friend}}》<ref>{{Cite web|last=Daw|first=Stephen|date=2021-01-14|title=Carole King, James Taylor & More to Perform at Joe Biden's 'We the People Concert'|url=http://www.billboard.com/amp/articles/news/9511644/carole-king-james-taylor-biden-we-the-people-concert|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118053414/https://www.billboard.com/amp/articles/news/9511644/carole-king-james-taylor-biden-we-the-people-concert|archive-date=2021-01-18|access-date=2021-01-18|website=www.billboard.com}}</ref>。墨西哥演员{{tsl|en|Jaime Camil|海梅·卡米尔}}就移民问题发表小演说，曾在2013年{{tsl|en|Second inauguration of Barack Obama|贝拉克·奥巴马第二次总统就职典礼}}表演的[[詹姆士·泰勒|詹姆士·泰勒]]演唱歌曲《[[美丽的阿美利加|美丽的阿美利加]]》<ref name=":10">{{Cite web|last=Brodsky|first=Rachel|date=2021-01-18|title=‘We The People’ concert: Connie Britton reveals moving moment with Joe Biden|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/news/we-the-people-concert-connie-britton-joe-biden-b1788704.html|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118053740/https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/news/we-the-people-concert-connie-britton-joe-biden-b1788704.html|archive-date=2021-01-18|access-date=2021-01-18|website=The Independent}}</ref><ref name="Schedule 12">{{cite news|date=2013-01-21|title=Barack Obama Presidential Inauguration: full schedule|work=Daily Telegraph|publisher=Joint Congressional Committee on Inaugural Ceremonies|location=London|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/barackobama/9815880/Barack-Obama-Presidential-Inauguration-full-schedule.html|dead-url=no|access-date=2013-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160428135003/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/barackobama/9815880/Barack-Obama-Presidential-Inauguration-full-schedule.html|archive-date=2016-04-28}}</ref>。演员{{le|康妮·布里顿|Connie Britton}}表达了政治团结的信念，回忆了她在2016年{{tsl|en|United State of Women Summit|美国妇女峰会}}见面的情形<ref name=":10" />。音乐团体[[打倒男孩|打倒男孩]]在预先录制的视频中表演歌曲《{{tsl|en|Centuries (song)|Centuries (歌曲)|Centuries}}》<ref name=":9" />。[[雪兒|雪兒]]之后就拜登和贺锦丽的胜出发表演讲，称自己对两人领导国家感到“兴奋、乐观”，然后翻唱[[麥莉·希拉|麥莉·希拉]]歌曲《{{tsl|en|I Hope You Find It|I Hope You Find It}}》<ref name=":5" />。演出最后，{{tsl|en|DJ Cassidy|DJ卡西迪}}向观众发表演说，并进行音乐采样<ref name=":9" />。

=== 国家志愿日 ===
就职日两天前的2021年1月18日是[[马丁·路德·金纪念日|马丁·路德·金纪念日]]，这一天是纪念[[马丁·路德·金|马丁·路德·金]]诞辰的联邦节假日。拜登和就职委员会鼓励民众当天参加社区礼拜活动，与{{le|AmeriCorps|AmeriCorps}}合作在全美筹划2500场线上或志愿活动<ref>{{cite news|last=Tamari|first=Jonathan|date=2021-01-18|title=Biden volunteered in Philly to mark Martin Luther King Jr. Day|publisher=The Inquirer|url=https://www.inquirer.com/politics/nation/joe-biden-philadelphia-martin-luther-king-jr-day-philabundance-20210118.html|dead-url=no|access-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118180522/https://www.inquirer.com/politics/nation/joe-biden-philadelphia-martin-luther-king-jr-day-philabundance-20210118.html|archive-date=2021-01-18}}</ref>。委员会建议社区举行志愿活动，为改善人民经济健康状态及社会福祉祈祷<ref>{{cite news|last=Saenz|first=Arlette|date=2021-01-04|title=Biden inaugural festivities to feature national day of service on MLK Day|publisher=CNN|url=https://www.cnn.com/2021/01/04/politics/biden-inauguration-day-of-service/index.html|dead-url=no|access-date=2021-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114194246/https://www.cnn.com/2021/01/04/politics/biden-inauguration-day-of-service/index.html|archive-date=2021-01-14}}</ref>，包括写卡片寄语疫情康复者、为无家可归者编织纪念品、开展“非接触式”捐助食品衣物所获服务及开展社区大清洁<ref>{{Cite web|last=VanHoose|first=Benjamin|date=2021-01-18|title=Biden Inauguration Committee Encourages Day of Service on Martin Luther King Jr. Day|url=https://people.com/politics/biden-inauguration-committee-day-of-service-martin-luther-king-jr-day/|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118170959/https://people.com/politics/biden-inauguration-committee-day-of-service-martin-luther-king-jr-day/|archive-date=2021-01-18|access-date=2021-01-18|website=PEOPLE}}</ref>。拜登伉俪当天在[[费城|费城]]非营利食物银行Philabundance打包[[罐头|罐头]]<ref>{{Cite web|last=|first=|date=2021-01-18|title=President-Elect Biden Volunteers at Philabundance for MLK Day of Service – NBC10 Philadelphia|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118165508/https://www.nbcphiladelphia.com/news/local/president-elect-biden-to-volunteer-at-philabundance-for-mlk-day-of-service/2671957/|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118165508/https://www.nbcphiladelphia.com/news/local/president-elect-biden-to-volunteer-at-philabundance-for-mlk-day-of-service/2671957/|archive-date=2021-01-18|access-date=2021-01-18|website=web.archive.org}}</ref>。贺锦丽伉俪在华盛顿特区参与志愿活动<ref>{{Cite web|last=Cohn|first=Alicia|date=2021-01-18|title=Biden calls Americans to volunteer on MLK Jr. Day|url=https://thehill.com/homenews/news/534663-biden-calls-americans-to-volunteer-on-mlk-jr-day|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118165801/https://thehill.com/homenews/news/534663-biden-calls-americans-to-volunteer-on-mlk-jr-day|archive-date=2021-01-18|access-date=2021-01-18|website=TheHill}}</ref>。

