=== 林肯纪念堂亮灯仪式 ===
1月19日晚，拜登于[[特拉华州|特拉华州]][[纽卡斯尔_(特拉华州)|纽卡斯尔]]{{le|特拉华州国民警卫队|Delaware National Guard|约瑟夫·R·“博”·拜登三世国民警卫队/预备役部队中心}}的欢送仪式上离开家乡特拉华州<ref name=APJan19>{{Cite web|authors=Lolita Baldor, James LaPorta, Lisa Mascaro and Jill Colvin|date=2021-01-19|title=The Latest:The Latest: Pence headed to Indiana after Biden inauguration|url=https://apnews.com/article/biden-inauguration-joe-biden-politics-ron-klain-mitch-mcconnell-45d78184ec204e0a775e0f38496ff67b|deadurl=no|agency=Associated Press|access-date=2021-01-19|archive-date=2021-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119180641/https://apnews.com/article/biden-inauguration-joe-biden-politics-ron-klain-mitch-mcconnell-45d78184ec204e0a775e0f38496ff67b}}</ref>。州长[[約翰·卡尼_(政治人物)|约翰·卡尼]]和拜登伉俪发表讲话，[[贝斯夏隆犹太会堂|贝斯夏隆犹太会堂]]拉比迈克尔·比尔斯（Michael S. Beals）发表祝祷<ref>{{Cite web|last=|first=|date=2021-01-19|title=Watch Live: Biden leaves Delaware for final time before inauguration|url=https://www.cbsnews.com/news/biden-inauguration-departs-wilmington-delaware-watch-live-stream-today-2021-01-19/|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119191115/https://www.cbsnews.com/news/biden-inauguration-departs-wilmington-delaware-watch-live-stream-today-2021-01-19/|archive-date=2021-01-19|access-date=2021-01-19|website=www.cbsnews.com}}</ref>。当天晚些时候，拜登伉俪和贺锦丽伉俪于{{tsl|en|Lincoln Memorial Reflecting Pool|林肯纪念堂倒影池}}参与全国亮灯仪式<ref name="Inauguration-Eve2">{{cite news|last=Allen|first=Mike|date=2020-12-31|title=Biden's plan for Inauguration Eve: Lights, church bells for COVID lives lost|work=Axios|url=https://www.axios.com/biden-memorial-covid-inauguration-d4addc1e-fa4c-4c4e-a3ed-f68b2fc060a7.html|dead-url=no|access-date=2020-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114194235/https://www.axios.com/biden-memorial-covid-inauguration-d4addc1e-fa4c-4c4e-a3ed-f68b2fc060a7.html|archive-date=2021-01-14}}</ref>。就职典礼组织方邀请全美各社区在就职典礼前夜（19日）东部时间晚5点30分点亮建筑，鸣响教堂钟声，纪念在疫情中去世的人士<ref name="Inauguration-Eve2">{{cite news|last=Allen|first=Mike|date=2020-12-31|title=Biden's plan for Inauguration Eve: Lights, church bells for COVID lives lost|work=Axios|url=https://www.axios.com/biden-memorial-covid-inauguration-d4addc1e-fa4c-4c4e-a3ed-f68b2fc060a7.html|dead-url=no|access-date=2020-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114194235/https://www.axios.com/biden-memorial-covid-inauguration-d4addc1e-fa4c-4c4e-a3ed-f68b2fc060a7.html|archive-date=2021-01-14}}</ref>。{{tsl|en|Lincoln Memorial Reflecting Pool|林肯纪念堂倒影池}}将同步举行亮灯仪式，帮助美国人在疫情过后重振精神<ref name="Inauguration-Eve2" />。拜登伉俪和哈里斯伉俪出席典礼<ref name=":19">{{Cite web|last=Falconer|first=Rebecca|date=2021-01-18|title=Empire State Building among hundreds to light up in Biden inauguration coronavirus tribute|url=https://www.axios.com/biden-inauguration-light-empire-state-building-covid-19-17aa86a0-654f-48a2-b6ee-a354757b72fd.html|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118172638/https://www.axios.com/biden-inauguration-light-empire-state-building-covid-19-17aa86a0-654f-48a2-b6ee-a354757b72fd.html|archive-date=2021-01-18|access-date=2021-01-18|website=Axios|11=}}</ref>。[[天主教華盛頓總教區|天主教華盛頓總教區]]枢机主教{{tsl|en|Wilton Daniel Gregory|威尔顿·丹尼尔·格雷戈里}}发表祈祷，福音歌手{{tsl|en|Yolanda Adams|尤兰达·亚当斯}}演唱歌曲《{{tsl|en|Hallelujah (Leonard Cohen song)|哈利路亚 (莱昂纳德·科恩歌曲)|哈利路亚}}》，密歇根州护士洛莉·玛丽·凯（Lori Marie Key）表演《[[奇异恩典|奇异恩典]]》。拜登和贺锦丽在致辞中强调全国哀悼活动的重要性，其中拜登表示这是“美国人疗愈的方法”<ref name="APJan19" />。[[帝国大厦|帝国大厦]]、[[太空针塔|太空针塔]]等主要城市及部落的国家地标举行亮灯仪式<ref name=":19" />。[[华盛顿国家座堂|华盛顿国家座堂]]鸣钟400下，纪念迄今为止在疫情中死亡的40万美国人<ref>{{Cite web|last=Castronuovo|first=Celine|date=2021-01-19|title=Washington National Cathedral to toll its bell 400 times to honor those lost to coronavirus|url=https://thehill.com/homenews/news/534826-washington-national-cathedral-will-toll-its-bell-400-times-to-honor-those-lost|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119230738/https://thehill.com/homenews/news/534826-washington-national-cathedral-will-toll-its-bell-400-times-to-honor-those-lost|archive-date=2021-01-19|access-date=2021-01-19|website=TheHill|11=}}</ref>。

