=== 纪念火车旅程 ===
拜登原计划乘坐[[美铁|美铁]]旅客列车从[[威尔明顿_(特拉华州)|威尔明顿]]前往华盛顿。值得一提的是，拜登在当参议员时经常坐这趟列车往返，故有“美铁乔”（Amtrak Joe）的外号。然而，出于安全考虑，这项计划被取消<ref name="ap-jm-biden-no-amtrak2">{{cite news|last1=Jaffe|first1=Alexandra|last2=Miller|first2=Zeke|date=2021-01-13|title=Biden forgoing Amtrak trip to Washington over security fears|agency=Associated Press|url=https://apnews.com/article/biden-inauguration-capitol-siege-joe-biden-donald-trump-ba7bcefad3a65bf9432e9178633baadd|dead-url=no|access-date=2021-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114194241/https://apnews.com/article/biden-inauguration-capitol-siege-joe-biden-donald-trump-ba7bcefad3a65bf9432e9178633baadd|archive-date=2021-01-14}}</ref>。2017年1月20日，拜登结束副总统任期后，乘坐[[阿西乐特快号列车|阿西乐特快号列车]]列车离开华盛顿，抵达[[威尔明顿站_(特拉华州)|威尔明顿站]]<ref>{{cite web|last=Cherry|first=Amy|date=2017-01-20|title=VIDEO: Crowd cheers, chants 'Welcome Home Joe' for the homecoming of Delaware's own|url=http://www.wdel.com/news/crowd-cheers-chants-welcome-home-joe-for-the-homecoming-of/article_2797b120-df52-11e6-8783-a78a028476d2.html|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114194254/https://www.wdel.com/news/crowd-cheers-chants-welcome-home-joe-for-the-homecoming-of/article_2797b120-df52-11e6-8783-a78a028476d2.html|archive-date=2021-01-14|access-date=2018-03-10|publisher=WDEL|location=Wilmington, DE}}</ref>。

=== 就职日礼拜 ===
拜登与夫人[[吉尔·拜登|吉尔·拜登]]于1月19日遵照新任总统的传统，在总统招待所[[布莱尔宫|布莱尔宫]]留宿<ref>{{Cite web|last=Phillips|first=Morgan|date=2021-01-13|title=White House offers and Biden accepts the use of Blair House for the night before inauguration|url=https://www.foxnews.com/politics/white-house-offers-biden-accepts-use-blair-house|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113202428/https://www.foxnews.com/politics/white-house-offers-biden-accepts-use-blair-house|archive-date=2021-01-13|access-date=2021-01-15|website=Fox News-US}}</ref>。一般当选总统和现任总统在就职当天早上的教堂礼拜后，会在白宫会面。然而当天拜登的日程表没有这项习俗，由于特朗普不会出席拜登的典礼，加上自{{tsl|en|2020 United States presidential debates#October 22 presidential debate (Belmont University)|2020年美国总统选举电视辩论|第二轮总统选举电视辩论}}没有和他直接沟通，这种传统不太可能得到维持<ref>{{Cite web|last=Miller|first=Zeke|date=2021-01-14|title=Lingering questions about how Trump will finish out his term|url=https://apnews.com/article/biden-inauguration-donald-trump-621ab28bd6f56242a05b0beb3284b036|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115031007/https://apnews.com/article/biden-inauguration-donald-trump-621ab28bd6f56242a05b0beb3284b036|archive-date=2021-01-15|access-date=2021-01-15|agency=Associated Press}}</ref>。此前拜登两次就任副总统时，都会出席{{tsl|en|Kevin F. O'Brien|凯文·奥布莱恩}}神父支持的天主教弥撒。2013年，这项活动在[[天文台环路一号|天文台环路一号]]副总统宅邸举行<ref>{{Cite web|last=Weissert|first=Will|last2=Schor|first2=Elena|date=2020-12-19|title=President in the pews: DC churches offer Biden options|url=https://apnews.com/article/joe-biden-coronavirus-pandemic-70e3ab48d7eefa4932f8c0c8eeb43e33|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110185554/https://apnews.com/article/70e3ab48d7eefa4932f8c0c8eeb43e33|archive-date=2021-01-10|access-date=2021-01-16|agency=Associated Press}}</ref>。拜登当天赴华盛顿[[圣玛窦主教座堂_(华盛顿)|圣玛窦主教座堂]]出席弥撒<ref name="Invite">{{Cite web|last=Wagner|first=John|last2=Min Kim|first2=Seung|authors=|date=2021-01-19|title=Biden invites congressional leadership to church on Wednesday|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/2021/01/19/inauguration-biden-trump-live-updates/#link-X22YIODMTZEZ7OVERTZW3EJGRE|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119183954/https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/2021/01/19/inauguration-biden-trump-live-updates/#link-X22YIODMTZEZ7OVERTZW3EJGRE|archive-date=2021-01-19|access-date=2021-01-19|website=|newspaper=Washington Post}}</ref>，参议院多数党领袖米奇·麦康奈尔、少数党领袖[[查克·舒默|查克·舒默]]、众议院议长南茜·佩洛西及众议院少数党领袖凯文·麦卡锡共四位国会两党领导人应邀出席<ref>{{Cite web|last=Budryk|first=Zack|date=2021-01-19|title=McConnnell, McCarthy accept Biden invitation to pre-inauguration church service|url=https://thehill.com/homenews/administration/534778-mcconnnell-mccarthy-accept-biden-invitation-to-pre-inauguration|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119184249/https://thehill.com/homenews/administration/534778-mcconnnell-mccarthy-accept-biden-invitation-to-pre-inauguration|archive-date=2021-01-19|access-date=2021-01-19|website=TheHill}}</ref>。

==== 特朗普欢送仪式 ====
就职典礼当天早上，特朗普从[[安德鲁斯联合基地|安德鲁斯联合基地]]乘坐[[空军一号|空军一号]]前往[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]][[棕榈滩|棕榈滩]]私人度假村[[海湖庄园|海湖庄园]]<ref name="WaltersBelam2">{{Cite web|author=Walters|first=Joanna|last2=Belam|first2=Martin|date=2021-01-18|title=Trump to hold early morning sendoff ceremony on Biden inauguration day|url=https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2021/jan/18/trump-sendoff-ceremony-biden-inauguration-day|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119105236/https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2021/jan/18/trump-sendoff-ceremony-biden-inauguration-day|archive-date=2021-01-19|access-date=2021-01-19|website=|newspaper=The Guardian}}</ref><ref name=":29">{{Cite web|last=|first=|date=2021-01-20|title=Air Force One Lifts Off With Trump Aboard After White House Departure, Ceremony|url=https://www.nbcwashington.com/news/trump-set-to-leave-white-house-early-wednesday/2546166/|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120142359/https://www.nbcwashington.com/news/trump-set-to-leave-white-house-early-wednesday/2546166/|archive-date=2021-01-20|access-date=2021-01-20|website=NBC4 Washington}}</ref>。特朗普与妻子、第一夫人[[梅拉尼娅·特朗普|梅拉尼娅·特朗普]]乘[[海军陆战队一号|海军陆战队一号]]直升飞机抵达，受到现场数百名支持者的欢迎。现场设红地毯，鸣21响礼炮，军乐团奏总统官方进行曲《[[向统帅致敬|向统帅致敬]]》<ref name=":28">{{Cite web|last=Colvin|first=Jill|date=2021-01-20|title=Trump leaves White House, says 'It's been a great honor'|url=https://apnews.com/article/biden-inauguration-joe-biden-capitol-siege-donald-trump-michael-pence-ad718c0048c341d0044c4709fb23c8dd|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120105602/https://apnews.com/article/biden-inauguration-joe-biden-capitol-siege-donald-trump-michael-pence-ad718c0048c341d0044c4709fb23c8dd|archive-date=2021-01-20|access-date=2021-01-20|website=Associated Press}}</ref>。特朗普在装有{{le|美国总统纹章|Seal of the President of the United States|总统纹章}}的讲台上发表短暂讲话，向人群表示“我们会以某种形式回归”<ref name=":28" /><ref name=":29" /><ref>{{Cite web|last=Crisp|first=Elizabeth|date=2021-01-20|title=Donald Trump, in final farewell speech, says "we will be back in some form"|url=https://www.newsweek.com/donald-trump-final-farewell-speech-says-we-will-back-some-form-1563025|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120143628/https://www.newsweek.com/donald-trump-final-farewell-speech-says-we-will-back-some-form-1563025|archive-date=2021-01-20|access-date=2021-01-20|website=Newsweek|11=}}</ref>。空军一号飞机升空时，现场响起了[[法蘭·仙納杜拉|法蘭·仙納杜拉]]的《[[My_Way|My Way]]》，这是四年前就职典礼舞会上，特朗普和妻子跳舞时的歌曲<ref name=":29" />。特朗普白宫团队曾邀请多位现任及前任政府官员出席活动，其中有[[麥菅當|麥菅當]]、[[約翰·法蘭西斯·凱利|約翰·法蘭西斯·凱利]]和[[安東尼·斯卡拉姆齊|安東尼·斯卡拉姆齊]]等一直批评特朗普的人士，但对方拒绝出席<ref>{{Cite web|last=Collins|first=Kaitlan|last2=Acosta|first2=Jim|last3=Liptak|first3=Kevin|last4=Bennett|first4=Kate|date=2021-01-19|title=Current and former officials who've been critical of Trump have been invited to his send-off|url=https://www.cnn.com/politics/live-news/biden-inauguration-dc-security-01-19-21/h_d44ef122c06b8d7f1338ad9bbabd162d|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119183747/https://www.cnn.com/politics/live-news/biden-inauguration-dc-security-01-19-21/h_d44ef122c06b8d7f1338ad9bbabd162d|archive-date=2021-01-19|access-date=2021-01-19|website=CNN|17=}}</ref><ref name="APJan192">{{Cite web|authors=Lolita Baldor, James LaPorta, Lisa Mascaro and Jill Colvin|date=2021-01-19|title=The Latest:The Latest: Pence headed to Indiana after Biden inauguration|url=https://apnews.com/article/biden-inauguration-joe-biden-politics-ron-klain-mitch-mcconnell-45d78184ec204e0a775e0f38496ff67b|dead-url=no|agency=Associated Press|access-date=2021-01-19|archive-date=2021-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119180641/https://apnews.com/article/biden-inauguration-joe-biden-politics-ron-klain-mitch-mcconnell-45d78184ec204e0a775e0f38496ff67b}}</ref>。他在一天前发表正式的{{tsl|en|Donald Trump's farewell address|唐纳德·特朗普的告别演说|告别演说}}，提到“新政府的就职典礼”，但没有提到乔·拜登的名字<ref>{{cite web |url=https://trumpwhitehouse.archives.gov/briefings-statements/remarks-president-trump-farewell-address-nation/ |title=Trump White House Archives — Briefings and Statements — Farewell Address |accessdate=2021-01-21 |archive-date=2021-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120194934/https://trumpwhitehouse.archives.gov/briefings-statements/remarks-president-trump-farewell-address-nation/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=|first=|date=2021-01-20|title=Biden inauguration: Trump leaves White House vowing 'we will be back'|work=BBC News|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-us-canada-55728852|dead-url=no|access-date=2021-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120202149/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-55728852|archive-date=2021-01-20}}</ref>。依照传统，特朗普在[[坚毅桌|坚毅桌]]上给拜登留了一封表示支持的信<ref>{{Cite web|last=Jackson|first=David|last2=Fritze|first2=John|date=2021-01-20|title=Donald Trump leaves letter for Joe Biden ahead of inauguration|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2021/01/20/donald-trump-leaves-letter-joe-biden-inauguration-day/4228139001/|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120152944/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2021/01/20/donald-trump-leaves-letter-joe-biden-inauguration-day/4228139001/|archive-date=2021-01-20|access-date=2021-01-20|website=USA TODAY}}</ref>。现任副总统彭斯也不出席欢送仪式，而是在参加完拜登就职典礼后回到家乡[[印第安纳州|印第安纳州]]，他的哥哥、印第安纳州国会议员{{tsl|en|Greg Pence|格雷格·彭斯}}与一众支持者到场迎接<ref name="APJan192" />。

====“为美国青年人喝彩”线上活动====
就职典礼前的两小时预热节目《我们的白宫：美国青年人庆祝就职典礼活动》（''Our White House: An Inaugural Celebration for Young Americans''）由演员{{tsl|en|Keke Palmer|琪琪·帕尔玛}}支持，吸引年轻人参与当天的活动<ref name="Youth">{{Cite web|last=Ali|first=Rasha|date=2021-01-16|title=Inauguration to include programming aimed at kids along with a message from Jill Biden|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/entertainment/tv/2021/01/16/jill-biden-make-appearance-during-inaugural-tv-programming/4192038001/|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117155608/https://www.usatoday.com/story/entertainment/tv/2021/01/16/jill-biden-make-appearance-during-inaugural-tv-programming/4192038001/|archive-date=2021-01-17|access-date=2021-01-18|agency=USA Today}}</ref>。节目中，拜登将向观众讲话，历史学家{{tsl|en|Doris Kearns Goodwin|多丽丝·凯恩斯·古德温}}和{{tsl|en|Erica Armstrong Dunbar|埃里卡·阿姆斯特朗·邓巴}}会解释典礼的历史意义。届时[[尼克儿童频道|尼克儿童频道]]将播出白宫宠物特辑，《[[PBS新闻一小时|PBS新闻一小时]]》播出学生专访及其他教育节目<ref name=Youth/>。

