n|first=Savannah|title=The Trumps, Jimmy Carter: Who did not attend Biden's inauguration|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2021/01/20/inauguration-who-wont-attendance-bidens-swearing/4167208001/|access-date=2021-01-21|website=USA TODAY|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124123754/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2021/01/20/inauguration-who-wont-attendance-bidens-swearing/4167208001/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=Creitz|first=Charles|date=2021-01-19|title=Former VP Quayle calls Trump absence from Biden inauguration 'unfortunate'|url=https://www.foxnews.com/politics/dan-quayle-trump-absence-biden-inauguration-unfortunate|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120013256/https://www.foxnews.com/politics/dan-quayle-trump-absence-biden-inauguration-unfortunate|archive-date=2021-01-20|access-date=2021-01-20|website=Fox News}}</ref>。[[美国最高法院|美国最高法院]]大法官[[克拉伦斯·托马斯|克拉伦斯·托马斯]]、[[塞繆爾·阿利托|塞繆爾·阿利托]]及最年长的法官[[史蒂芬·布雷耶|史蒂芬·布雷耶]]因疫情带来的健康风险未出席，另外六人则出席，是最高法院大法官近20年来首次未集体出席就职典礼<ref>Robert Barnes, [https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/courts_law/thomas-alito-breyer-missed-biden-inaguration/2021/01/20/726d7554-5b63-11eb-8bcf-3877871c819d_story.html An incomplete Supreme Court witnessed Biden's oath. There's history there.] {{Wayback|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/courts_law/thomas-alito-breyer-missed-biden-inaguration/2021/01/20/726d7554-5b63-11eb-8bcf-3877871c819d_story.html |date=20210122012311 }}, ''Washington Post'' (January 20, 2021).</ref>。多位{{tsl|en|ambassadors to the United States|驻美大使}}出席典礼<ref>{{Cite web|last=|first=|last2=|last3=|first3=|date=2021-01-21|title=India's Ambassador to US attends Biden's inauguration ceremony {{!}} India News - Times of India|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/indias-ambassador-to-us-attends-bidens-inauguration-ceremony/articleshow/80377895.cms|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121045620/https://timesofindia.india