[[File:Joe_Biden_takes_the_presidential_oath_of_office.webm|thumb]][[約翰·羅伯茨|約翰·羅伯茨]]监誓下宣誓]]宣誓完成，{{le|美国陆军军乐团|United States Army Band}}演奏崇戎乐，但未有21响礼炮致敬，导致拜登发表就职演说前的程序稍微延迟。后来拜登在阿灵顿国家公墓敬献花圈时，21响礼炮鸣响<ref>Stephanie Sigafoos, [https://www.mcall.com/news/breaking/mc-nws-joe-biden-presidential-inauguration-need-to-know-20210119-r2g2m2ylpfgyzktecofgde25hq-story.html Inauguration Day: How to watch, what to expect as Joe Biden is sworn in as president] {{Wayback|url=https://www.mcall.com/news/breaking/mc-nws-joe-biden-presidential-inauguration-need-to-know-20210119-r2g2m2ylpfgyzktecofgde25hq-story.html |date=20210119152808 }}, ''Morning Call'' (January 19, 2021).</ref>。用于授权发动核袭击的总统[[核足球|核足球]]被送出指挥中心，在典礼期间秘密移交给新政府军方人员；尽管特朗普缺席典礼，核足球密码还是自动撤销了他和彭斯的访问密码，转移给拜登和贺锦丽<ref>{{Cite web|last=Cohen|first=Zachary|date=2021-01-19|title=How Trump will hand off the 'nuclear football' to Biden|url=https://www.cnn.com/2021/01/19/politics/trump-biden-nuclear-football-inauguration/index.html|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119165739/https://www.cnn.com/2021/01/19/politics/trump-biden-nuclear-football-inauguration/index.html|archive-date=2021-01-19|access-date=2021-01-19|website=CNN}}</ref>。

====就职演说====
拜登就职演说长达21分钟，提到他计划在2019冠状病毒病、{{tsl|en|Economic impact of the COVID-19 pandemic in the United States|2019冠状病毒病美国的经济影响|经济冲突}}、[[全球变暖|全球变暖]]、[[政治极化|政治极化]]和{{le|美国种族不平等|Racial inequality in the United States|种族不平等}}的多重影响下，团结整个国家<ref>{{Cite news|last=Ashraf|first=Khalil|date=2020-12-15|title=Biden to take oath outside Capitol amid virus restrictions|work=The Washington Post|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/biden-to-take-oath-outside-capitol-amid-virus-restrictions/2020/12/15/16e6d326-3f00-11eb-b58b-1623f6267960_story.html|dead-url=no|access-date=2020-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114194342/https://www.washingtonpost.com/|archive-date=2021-01-14}}</ref>。拜登在演讲家{{tsl|en|Vinay Reddy|维奈·雷迪}}、高级顾问{{tsl|en|Mike Donilon|迈克·多尼隆}}、候任国务卿[[安東尼·布林肯|安東尼·布林肯]]和幕僚长[[罗恩·克莱恩|罗恩·克莱恩]]的协助下撰写讲稿<ref>{{Cite news|last=Korecki|first=Natascha|date=2021-01-19|title=Writing a speech for Biden can be hell. And that was before the inaugural.|publisher=Politico|url=https://www.politico.com/news/2021/01/19/joe-biden-inaugural-speech-lincoln-460506|dead-url=no|access-date=2021-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120051658/https://www.politico.com/news/2021/01/19/joe-biden-inaugural-speech-lincoln-460506|archive-date=2021-01-20}}</ref>。《纽约时报》认为他的演说在语气上“直接反驳”了特朗普的就职演说（特朗普提到了“美国大屠杀”），呼吁拥抱多样性，终结政治、人口分布及意识形态等美国文化的“冷内战”，以此促使美国人“打开心扉，而不是变得铁石心肠”<ref name=":31">{{Cite news|last=Baker|first=Peter|last2=Astor|first2=Maggie|last3=Kaplan|first3=Thomas|date=2021-01-20|title=Inauguration Live Updates: President Biden Arrives at the White House|work=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/live/2021/01/20/us/biden-inauguration|dead-url=no|access-date=2021-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120181241/https://www.nytimes.com/live/2021/01/20/us/biden-inauguration|archive-date=2021-01-20|issn=0362-4331}}</ref>。

演讲中，拜登多番重复他的竞选誓言“为支持我和不支持我的人付出同等的努力”<ref name=":33">{{Cite web|last=Staff|first=NPR|date=2021-01-20|title='This Is America's Day': Biden's Inaugural Address, Annotated|url=https://www.npr.org/2021/01/20/956922884/bidens-inaugural-address-annotated|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120201236/https://www.npr.org/2021/01/20/956922884/bidens-inaugural-address-annotated|archive-date=2021-01-20|access-date=2021-01-20|website=NPR.org|11=}}</ref><ref name=":34">{{Cite web|last=Wise|first=Alana|date=2021-01-20|title=Biden Celebrates 'Triumph' Of Democracy In Inaugural Address|url=https://www.npr.org/sections/inauguration-day-live-updates/2021/01/20/958793060/biden-celebrates-triumph-of-democracy-in-inaugural-address|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120231050/https://www.npr.org/sections/inauguration-day-live-updates/2021/01/20/958793060/biden-celebrates-triumph-of-democracy-in-inaugural-address|archive-date=2021-01-20|access-date=2021-01-20|website=NPR.org|11=}}</ref>。他公开谴责[[造谣|造谣]]，以及将造谣武器化、从中获取利益的政客，从而隐晦指责了在任期间[[唐纳德·特朗普言论的真实性|制造大量假消息]]的特朗普<ref name=":31" />。拜登明确谴责[[白人优越主义|白人优越主义]]和[[排外主义|排外主义]]，指两者是美国人的“丑恶一面”，且为《[[美国独立宣言|美国独立宣言]]》提到的“美式理想”—[[人皆生而平等|人皆生而平等]]—蒙上阴霾<ref name=":31" /><ref name=":33" /><ref>{{Cite web|last=Lemire|first=Jonathan|last2=Miller|first2=Zeke|last3=Jaffe|first3=Alexandria|date=2021-01-20|title=Biden takes the helm as president: 'Democracy has prevailed'|url=https://apnews.com/article/joe-biden-inauguration-a01d1ffa7862661914cb92b22e359854|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120212756/https://apnews.com/article/joe-biden-inauguration-a01d1ffa7862661914cb92b22e359854|archive-date=2021-01-20|access-date=2021-01-20|website=Associated Press}}</ref>。演讲还提到贺锦丽升任副总统的历史意义，并回顾了允许非裔美国人和女性参政的[[非裔美国人民权运动|民权运动]]和[[女性参政权|女性参政权]]。拜登称他就任美国总统是民主的“胜利”；表示虽然就在短短两周前，刚刚发生了冲击国会的暴动，但今天仍然实现了[[政党轮替|和平权力交接]]<ref name=":34" /><ref name=":33" />。

=== 典礼后活动===
[[File:Passinreviewbiden.jpg|link=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Passinreviewbiden.jpg]][[美军|部队]]]]
宣誓仪式后，拜登、贺锦丽与配偶在国会东翼[[阅兵|检阅]][[美军|部队]]。一般在阅兵仪式前，新任总统会为乘坐[[海军陆战队一号|海军陆战队一号]]离开华盛顿的卸任总统送行<ref name=":8">{{Cite web|last=Subramanian|first=Courtney|last2=Fritze|first2=John|last3=Jackson|first3=David|date=2021-01-15|title=Trump to hold departure ceremony at Joint Base Andrews on morning of Biden inauguration|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2021/01/15/trump-hold-departure-ceremony-morning-biden-inauguration/4178260001/|deadurl=yes|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123093105/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2021/01/15/trump-hold-departure-ceremony-morning-biden-inauguration/4178260001/|archive-date=2021-01-23|access-date=2021-01-16|website=USA TODAY}}</ref>。然而特朗普在拜登就职典礼开始前就会离开，故这项传统被打破。在场的卸任副总统[[迈克·彭斯|迈克·彭斯]]则由现任副总统贺锦丽与[[美國第二夫人及先生|第二先生]][[任德龙|任德龙]]送别。自1897年{{tsl|en|First inauguration of William McKinley|威廉·麦金莱第一次总统就职典礼}}起开始的国会午餐会因公众健康考虑取消<ref>{{Cite news|last=Korte|first=Gregory|date=2020-12-29|title=Biden’s Inaugural Lunch Called Off Due to Concern Over Virus|agency=Bloomberg News|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-12-29/biden-s-inaugural-lunch-called-off-due-to-concern-over-virus|dead-url=no|access-date=2020-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106014820/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-12-29/biden-s-inaugural-lunch-called-off-due-to-concern-over-virus|archive-date=2021-01-06}}</ref>。然而，拜登和贺锦丽在{{le|美国国会圆形大厅|United States Capitol rotunda|圆形大厅}}向公众展出多个纪念品，包括{{tsl|en|Robert S. Duncanson|罗伯特·S·邓肯森}}的画作《彩虹景图》（Landscape with Rainbow）、{{le|Lenox|Lenox (company}}公司彼得·奥罗克（Peter O'Rourke）切割的两个[[铅|铅]]制水晶花瓶、两面就职典礼期间在国会上空飘扬的国旗，以及两人的正式画像<ref>{{Cite web|last=Schiller|first=Meghan|date=2021-01-19|title=Pittsburgh-Area Glass Cutter Handcrafts Special Inauguration Gifts For Joe Biden And Kamala Harris|url=https://pittsburgh.cbslocal.com/2021/01/19/glass-cutter-handcrafts-inauguration-gifts-for-presidents-vice-presidents/|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121190543/https://pittsburgh.cbslocal.com/2021/01/19/glass-cutter-handcrafts-inauguration-gifts-for-presidents-vice-presidents/|archive-date=2021-01-21|access-date=2021-01-20|website=}}</ref>。中午，拜登参加行政命令签署仪式，向国会签署《就职典礼日宣言》（Inauguration Day Proclamation）及其对内阁及副内阁职位人选的提名<ref>{{Cite web|last=|first=|author-link=|authors=Meg Wagner, Melissa Mahtani, Melissa Macaya, Mike Hayes, Veronica Rocha and Fernando Alfonso III|date=2021-01-20|title=Biden Inauguration Day: Live coverage of Joe Biden, Kamala Harris and the US Capitol ceremony|url=https://www.cnn.com/politics/live-news/biden-harris-inauguration-day-2021/index.html|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125024141/https://www.cnn.com/politics/live-news/biden-harris-inauguration-day-2021/index.html|archive-date=2021-01-25|access-date=2021-01-20|website=CNN|13=}}</ref>。晚上，在贺锦丽的监督下，于1月6日乔治亚州{{le|2020–21年乔治亚州美国参议院选举|2020–21 United States Senate election in Georgia|参议员常规选举}}和{{tsl|en|2020–21 United States Senate special election in Georgia|2020–21年乔治亚州美国参议院补选|补选}}中当选的[[乔恩·奥索夫|乔恩·奥索夫]]和众议员[[拉斐尔·沃诺克|拉斐尔·沃诺克]]宣誓就任，两人的胜选使得[[民主党_(美国)|民主党]]成为参议院多数党。另外，她会为[[加利福尼亚州州长列表|加州州长]][[加文·纽森|加文·纽森]]提名、填补她空缺席位的参议员[[亚历克斯·帕迪利亚|亚历克斯·帕迪利亚]]监誓<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-election-georgia/democrats-to-take-working-control-of-us-senate-wednesday-when-three-sworn-in-idUSKBN29O2BV|title=Democrats to take working control of U.S. Senate Wednesday when three sworn in|last=Cornwell|first=Susan|publisher=[[路透社|Reuters]]|date=2021-01-19|access-date=2021-01-20|archive-date=2021-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120064941/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-election-georgia/democrats-to-take-working-control-of-us-senate-wednesday-when-three-sworn-in-idUSKBN29O2BV|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==== 阿灵顿国家公墓献花仪式 ====
[[File:President_Joseph_R._Biden,_Jr._and_Vice_President_Kamala_Harris_participated_in_a_Presidential_Armed_Forces_Full_Honors_Wreath-Laying_Ceremony_at_the_Tomb_of_the_Unknown_Soldier_at_Arlington_National_Cemetery_(50857647541).jpg|thumb]]{{le|无名烈士墓 (阿灵顿)|Tomb of the Unknown Soldier (Arlington)|无名烈士墓}}敬献花圈]]
阅兵仪式后，拜登和贺锦丽和克林顿、布什及奥巴马等一众前总统伉俪，前往[[阿灵顿国家公墓|阿灵顿国家公墓]]{{tsl|en|Tomb of the Unknown Soldier (Arlington)|无名烈士墓 (阿灵顿)|无名烈士墓}}[[花环|献花圈]]<ref name=":4">{{Cite news|url=https://www.nbcnews.com/politics/white-house/biden-plans-america-united-inauguration-theme-n1253715|title=Biden plans 'America United' inauguration theme|last=Edelman|first=Adam|agency=NBC News|date=2021-01-11|access-date=2021-01-11|archive-date=2021-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114194313/https://www.nbcnews.com/politics/white-house/biden-plans-america-united-inauguration-theme-n1253715|dead-url=no}}</ref>。据总统历史学家{{tsl|en|Timothy Naftali|蒂莫西·纳夫塔利}}介绍，这项传统自1921年{{tsl|en|Inauguration of Warren G. Harding|沃伦·盖玛利尔·哈定就职典礼}}开始，迄今已有100年的历史<ref name=":30">{{Cite web|last=Ryan|first=Josiah|date=2021-01-20|title=Biden Inauguration Day: Live coverage of Joe Biden, Kamala Harris and the US Capitol ceremony|url=https://www.cnn.com/politics/live-news/biden-harris-inauguration-day-2021/index.html|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120203210/https://edition.cnn.com/politics/live-news/biden-harris-inauguration-day-2021/index.html|archive-date=2021-01-20|access-date=2021-01-20|website=CNN|11=}}</ref>，在“国家焦虑、痛苦和经受磨难的时候”，拜登和前几位总统纪念在战争中死去的无名烈士，“传达了团结的视觉信息”<ref name=":30" />。

====网络直播游行====
[[File:Biden_inaugural_parade.jpg|left]]]]
鲜花仪式过后，[[宾夕法尼亚大道|宾夕法尼亚大道]]举行欢送拜登和贺锦丽入主白宫的游行活动，美军各军种、拜登母校[[特拉华大学|特拉华大学]]和贺锦丽母校[[霍华德大学|霍华德大学]]鼓乐队参与<ref name=":20">{{Cite web|last=Collins|first=Michael|date=2021-01-18|title=Joe Biden's virtual 'Parade Across America' to feature 'heroes' and Jon Stewart, Andra Day, Kenny Ortega|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2021/01/18/biden-inauguration-virtual-parade-replaces-pennsylvania-ave-parade/4201809001/|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118224752/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2021/01/18/biden-inauguration-virtual-parade-replaces-pennsylvania-ave-parade/4201809001/?itm_source=AMP&itm_medium=UpNext|archive-date=2021-01-18|access-date=2021-01-18|website=USA TODAY}}</ref><ref name=":21">{{Cite web|last=Mitchell|first=Samantha|date=2021-01-18|title=Howard University Drumline to perform during the Inaugural 'Parade Across America'|url=https://wjla.com/news/local/howard-university-drumline-to-perform-during-the-inaugural-parade-across-america|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118225241/https://wjla.com/news/local/howard-university-drumline-to-perform-during-the-inaugural-parade-across-america|archive-date=2021-01-18|access-date=2021-01-18|website=WJLA}}</ref>。拜登就职委员会组织的《全美线上游行》（Virtual Parade Across America）同步播出，由演员[[托尼·戈德溫|托尼·戈德溫]]主持，用音乐、诗歌、舞蹈等节目展现美国的文化种族多样性及韧性<ref name="Biden-Parade">{{Cite news|last=Collins|first=Michael|date=2021-01-03|title=Joe Biden to get 'presidential escort' to White House, virtual parade instead of traditional inaugural festivities|work=[[今日美國|USA Today]]|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2021/01/03/inauguration-biden-get-escort-white-house-virtual-parade/4120484001/|dead-url=no|access-date=2021-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114194238/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2021/01/03/inauguration-biden-get-escort-white-house-virtual-parade/4120484001/|archive-date=2021-01-14}}</ref><ref name=":20" />。白宫外原计划为就职游行搭建的观礼台最终因计划改变拆除<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2020/12/30/biden-inauguration-parade-viewing-stands-near-white-house-dismantled/4085710001/|title=Parade viewing stands dismantled near White House as Biden team seeks to discourage inauguration crowds|last=Brown|first=Matthew|work=[[今日美國|USA Today]]|date=2020-12-30|access-date=2020-12-31|archive-date=2021-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114194241/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2020/12/30/biden-inauguration-parade-viewing-stands-near-white-house-dismantled/4085710001/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。现场游行仪式由{{tsl|en|Charlie Brotman|查理·布罗特曼}}开场，自前总统[[德怀特·艾森豪威尔|德怀特·艾森豪威尔]]{{le|德怀特·艾森豪威尔第二次总统就职典礼|Second inauguration of Dwight D. Eisenhower|第二次就职典礼}}起，他一直担任游行报幕员<ref name="APJan19" /><ref name="washpost">{{cite news|last=Kunkle|first=Fredrick|date=2013-01-20|title=Inaugural parade's announcer knows how to call 'em as voice of former Washington Senators ballclub|newspaper=Washington Post|location=Washington DC|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/national/inauguration/inaugural-parades-announcer-knows-how-to-call-em-as-voice-of-old-senators-team/2013/01/20/945829ac-6279-11e2-b05a-605528f6b712_story.html|dead-url=no|accessdate=2021-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180802152340/https://www.washingtonpost.com/national/inauguration/inaugural-parades-announcer-knows-how-to-call-em-as-voice-of-old-senators-team/2013/01/20/945829ac-6279-11e2-b05a-605528f6b712_story.html|archive-date=2018-08-02}}</ref>。

喜剧演员[[喬恩·史都華|喬恩·史都華]]，音乐人安德烈·戴（Andra Day）、{{tsl|en|Nile Rodgers|尼罗·罗杰斯}}和{{tsl|en|Kathy Sledge|凯西·史赖吉}}与多个合唱队及多名运动员（包括前奥运选手[[陈巍|陈巍]]、[[艾麗森·菲利克斯|艾麗森·菲利克斯]]和[[姬蒂·雷德基|姬蒂·雷德基]]）参与“线上点名”<ref name=":20" /><ref>{{Cite web|last=Allen|first=Mike|date=2021-01-19|title=Biden's virtual "Parade Across America" to feature 1,391 people, 90 horses, 9 dogs|url=https://www.axios.com/biden-virtual-inauguration-parade-342f53e0-402b-4d3c-93cd-c87ac493f4d0.html|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119202522/https://www.axios.com/biden-virtual-inauguration-parade-342f53e0-402b-4d3c-93cd-c87ac493f4d0.html|archive-date=2021-01-19|access-date=2021-01-19|website=Axios|11=}}</ref>。仪式共动用1391名线上参与者、95匹马和9条狗<ref name="APJan19" />。仪式期间，于疫情期间帮助社区的前线医护工作者及多位杰出学生老师获颁“英雄”称号<ref name=":20" />。编舞[[肯尼·奥特加|肯尼·奥特加]]与全国275名事先录制视频的舞蹈者一起舞蹈<ref name=":21" />；轮椅篮球计划莱恩·马丁基金会（Ryan Martin Foundation）参加线上游行<ref name=":20" />。典礼最后，音乐团体激进小子20年来首次合体，献唱金曲《You Get What You Give》<ref name=":3">{{Cite web|last=Kreps|first=Daniel|last2=|first2=|date=2021-01-18|title=New Radicals to Reunite for First Time in 22 Years for Biden Inauguration Parade|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/new-radicals-reunion-biden-inauguration-parade-1115838/|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118051308/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/new-radicals-reunion-biden-inauguration-parade-1115838/|archive-date=2021-01-18|access-date=2021-01-18|website=Rolling Stone}}</ref>。这首歌被贺锦丽丈夫任德龙在2020年的竞选集会中使用，也在拜登自传《{{le|答应我，父亲|Promise Me, Dad}}》有所提及，指这首歌在他的已故儿子博与[[胶质母细胞瘤|胶质母细胞瘤]]晚期作斗争时，是家庭聚会的“主题曲”<ref name=":3" />。乐队队长{{tsl|en|Gregg Alexander|格雷格·亚历山大}}希望这首歌能够在“这样黑暗的时候点燃最微弱的灯塔”<ref name=":3" />。

====《庆祝美国》特别节目====
传统的{{le|美国总统就职舞会|United States presidential inaugural balls|就职舞会}}一般会有数百名来宾前来见总统，持续至深夜，但今年的仪式因疫情原因取消，改为黄金时段电视特别节目《庆祝美国》（''Celebrating America''）。节目在全美主流电视台和其他有线电视及流媒体平台直播，由[[汤姆·汉克斯|汤姆·汉克斯]]主持。节目开始，[[布魯斯·斯普林斯汀|布魯斯·斯普林斯汀]]在林肯纪念堂台阶上演唱《{{tsl|en|Land of Hope and Dreams|希望和梦想之地}}》<ref name=":03">{{Cite web|last=Lejeune|first=Tristan|date=2021-01-20|title=Bruce Springsteen kicks off 'Celebrating America' special with 'Land of Hope and Dreams'|url=https://thehill.com/blogs/in-the-know/in-the-know/535150-bruce-springsteen-kicks-off-celebrating-america-special-with|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121031546/https://thehill.com/blogs/in-the-know/in-the-know/535150-bruce-springsteen-kicks-off-celebrating-america-special-with|archive-date=2021-01-21|access-date=2021-01-20|website=TheHill|11=}}</ref>。之后汉斯向观众讲话，强调“我们这片应许之地的承诺”，并介绍四位嘉宾[[卡里姆·阿卜杜勒-贾巴尔|卡里姆·阿卜杜勒-贾巴尔]]、{{tsl|en|Dolores Huerta|多洛雷斯·韦尔塔}}、{{tsl|en|Brayden Harrington|布赖登·哈灵顿}}和[[伍佩琴|伍佩琴]]，私人分别朗诵总统林肯、罗斯福、肯尼迪和里根就职讲话部分内容，体现他们的讲话强调举国团结、自信、爱国和和平。

弗吉尼亚州[[联合包裹服务|联合包裹服务]]（UPS）[[宅配|快递员]]安东尼·加斯金（Anthony Gaskin）介绍[[瓊·邦·喬飛|瓊·邦·喬飛]]，乔飞不插电翻唱了[[披头士|披头士]]的《[[Here_Comes_the_Sun|Here Comes the Sun]]》。汉克斯之后介绍新总统拜登，他在美国海军军乐团吹奏四段崇戎樂和《向统帅致敬》后，于林肯纪念堂内发表讲话，强调“机会、自由、尊严和尊重”的重要性。[[马友友|马友友]]大提琴演奏《[[奇异恩典|奇异恩典]]》、《[[第9號交響曲_(德沃夏克)|德沃夏克第9号交响曲]]》选段《Goin' Home》和《{{tsl|en|Simple Gifts|Simple Gifts}}》。{{le|安特·克莱蒙斯|Ant Clemons}}和[[賈斯汀·提姆布萊克|賈斯汀·提姆布萊克]]在[[田纳西州|田纳西州]][[孟菲斯_(田纳西州)|孟菲斯]]演唱歌曲《Better Days》<ref>{{Cite web|last=|first=|date=2021-01-20|title=Ant Clemons on Performing ‘Better Days' with Justin Timberlake During the Inauguration Special|url=https://www.nbclosangeles.com/entertainment/ant-clemons-on-performing-better-days-with-justin-timberlake-during-the-inauguration-special/2509599/|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121031827/https://www.nbclosangeles.com/entertainment/ant-clemons-on-performing-better-days-with-justin-timberlake-during-the-inauguration-special/2509599/|archive-date=2021-01-21|access-date=2021-01-21|website=NBC Los Angeles}}</ref>。华盛顿小学教师麦肯齐·亚当斯（Mackenzie Adams）随后介绍[[喷火战机乐队|喷火战机乐队]]，主唱[[戴夫·格羅爾|戴夫·格羅爾]]在表演开场提到老师们在疫情期间利用“创意”解决教学方法上的挑战，之后乐队表演《{{tsl|en|Times Like These (song)|Times Like These}}》<ref name=":110">{{Cite web|last=Weprin|first=Alex|date=2021-01-13|title=Tom Hanks Hosting 'Celebrating America' Inaugural Special With Performances From Demi Lovato & More|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/9510519/celebrating-america-hosted-tom-hanks-lineup-demi-lovato|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113161326/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/9510519/celebrating-america-hosted-tom-hanks-lineup-demi-lovato/|archive-date=2021-01-13|access-date=2021-01-15|website=Billboard|11=}}</ref>。百老汇群星游行队伍表演《{{tsl|en|Seasons of Love|Seasons of Love}}》和《Let the Sun Shine In》。

热心公益的厨师{{tsl|en|José Andrés|何塞·安德列斯}}介绍美国的{{tsl|en|Impact of the COVID-19 pandemic on the food industry|2019冠状病毒病疫情对食品工业的影响|食品短缺危机}}，介绍在网上开{{tsl|en|lemonade stand|柠檬水摊}}、为饥饿的人士筹款5.2万美元的威斯康辛小学生梅根·马什-麦格隆（Morgan Marsh-McGlone）。[[林-曼努爾·米蘭達|林-曼努爾·米蘭達]]随后朗诵爱尔兰诗人[[谢默斯·希尼|谢默斯·希尼]]的诗歌《{{tsl|en|The Cure at Troy|The Cure at Troy}}》<ref>{{Cite web|last=Chamlee|first=Virginia|date=2021-01-18|title=Lin-Manuel Miranda Joins Kareem Abdul-Jabbar, José Andrés and More for Biden Inaugural Special|url=https://people.com/politics/lin-manuel-miranda-biden-inaugural-special/|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118182819/https://people.com/politics/lin-manuel-miranda-biden-inaugural-special/|archive-date=2021-01-18|access-date=2021-01-18|website=PEOPLE.com|11=}}</ref>，这首诗曾被拜登于2020年民主党全国大会的演说中引用。[[国际空间站|国际空间站]][[远征64|远征64]]任务的美国成员随后从太空向观众发来问候。首位参与[[五强联盟|五强联盟]]橄榄球比赛的女性运动员{{tsl|en|Sarah Fuller (athlete)|莎拉·福勒}}介绍副总统贺锦丽，在四段崇戎樂和《向统帅致敬》后，她发表讲话，形容美国人“大胆、无畏、雄心勃勃”，举了[[阿波罗11号|阿波罗11号]]登月活动、民权及妇女参政运动的例子。其后[[约翰·传奇|约翰·传奇]]翻唱歌曲《{{tsl|en|Feeling Good|Feeling Good}}》<ref name=":110" />。

首个接种[[BNT162|辉瑞联合BioNTech研发2019冠状病毒病疫苗]]的美国人、护士桑德拉·林赛（Sandra Lindsay）介绍{{tsl|en|Tyler Hubbard|泰勒·哈伯德}}和[[提姆·麥克羅|提姆·麥克羅]]，两人在[[纳什维尔|纳什维尔]]的一处屋顶演唱两人合作的歌曲《Undivided》<ref>{{Cite web|last=Freeman|first=Jon|last2=|first2=|date=2021-01-19|title=Tim McGraw, Tyler Hubbard to Perform on Joe Biden's Inauguration TV Special|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-country/tim-mcgraw-tyler-hubbard-biden-inauguration-special-1116322/|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119182521/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-country/tim-mcgraw-tyler-hubbard-biden-inauguration-special-1116322/|archive-date=2021-01-19|access-date=2021-01-19|website=Rolling Stone}}</ref>。前总统克林顿、布什和奥巴马亮相{{tsl|en|Arlington Memorial Amphitheater|阿灵顿纪念露天剧场}}，强调美国团结的重要性，回忆他们见证的权利交接，表达对拜登和贺锦丽的支持。[[黛咪·洛瓦托|黛咪·洛瓦托]]演唱[[比爾·威瑟斯|比爾·威瑟斯]]歌曲《{{tsl|en|Lovely Day|Lovely Day}}》，感谢前线医护人员<ref name=":110" />。节目最后，[[凱蒂·佩芮|凱蒂·佩芮]]演唱歌曲《[[煙火_(單曲)|烟火]]》，同时华盛顿纪念碑举行[[烟火|烟火]]表演，拜登伉俪和贺锦丽伉俪在白宫和林肯纪念堂观看<ref name=":03" />。

==示威活动==
{{Main|{{le|2021年美国国会抗议|2021 United States capitol protests}}}}
2020年总统选举结果引发的连串示威和反示威运动于2020年12月开始<ref>{{cite news|last1=Khalil|first1=Ashraf|date=2020-12-12|title=Trump loyalists converging again on Washington over election|agency=Associated Press|url=https://apnews.com/article/election-2020-donald-trump-politics-elections-8a505d0ae0915e0c9297208a76d7838a|dead-url=no|access-date=2020-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114194322/https://apnews.com/article/election-2020-donald-trump-politics-elections-8a505d0ae0915e0c9297208a76d7838a|archive-date=2021-01-14}}</ref>。

1月6日美国国会遭袭后，哥伦比亚特区市长穆丽儿·鲍泽要求[[美国内政部|内政部]]取消华盛顿特区抗议活动的申请，拒绝就职典礼期间的示威活动申请<ref name=":4" /><ref name="KnickmeyerKhalil">{{Cite web|last=Knickmeyer|first=Ellen|last2=Khalil|first2=Ashraf|date=2021-01-15|title=Trump supporters among those seeking Jan. 20 protest permits|url=https://apnews.com/article/biden-inauguration-joe-biden-donald-trump-politics-muriel-bowser-9573f6710a28e5acadf5f0ba3a851c6d|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117001019/https://apnews.com/article/biden-inauguration-joe-biden-donald-trump-politics-muriel-bowser-9573f6710a28e5acadf5f0ba3a851c6d|archive-date=2021-01-17|access-date=2021-01-18|website=Associated Press}}</ref>，但被内政部拒绝<ref name=KnickmeyerKhalil/>。尽管国家广场在典礼期间停止开放，国家公园局还是安排临近的两个公园{{tsl|en|John Marshall Park|约翰·马歇尔公园}}和{{tsl|en|Navy Memorial|海军纪念碑}}，专门让公众举行“[[美国宪法第一修正案|第一修正案]]活动”（即抗议）<ref name=NewWarnings/><ref name=RecordDetermination>[https://www.nps.gov/nama/learn/management/namacloserod.htm Record of Determination for the Partial Temporary Closure of Areas within and around the National Mall in Response to Threats to Visitors and Park Resources] {{Wayback|url=https://www.nps.gov/nama/learn/management/namacloserod.htm |date=20210115175135 }}, National Park Service (January 16, 2021).</ref>。美国公园警察依照最近社会事件及眼下的威胁评估做出该决定，而上述各公园最多只容纳100人<ref name=RecordDetermination/>，进入指定区域的人士需要接受[[磁强计|金属探测器]]检查<ref name=KnickmeyerKhalil/>。左翼团体{{tsl|en|A.N.S.W.E.R.|ANSWER联盟}}和DC行动实验室（DC Action Lab）获得抗议许可，双方同意遵守观众规则举行示威活动<ref name=KnickmeyerKhalil/>。另外亲特朗普团体“为特朗普咆哮”（Roar for Trump）和“女性为伟大美国”（Women for a Great America）也申请示威<ref name=Nov2020>{{Cite news|url=https://wtop.com/dc/2020/11/inauguration-day-plans-begin-in-dc-but-still-many-question-marks/|title=Inauguration Day plans begin in DC, but still many question marks|first=Megan|last=Cloherty|date=2020-11-10|publisher=WTOP-FM|access-date=2021-01-13|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112023445/https://wtop.com/dc/2020/11/inauguration-day-plans-begin-in-dc-but-still-many-question-marks/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

情报部门估计就职典礼当天美国国会及多个州议会会爆发大规模抗议和武装民兵游行，但示威活动规模实际上比较小。当天，[[纽约州议会大厦|纽约州议会大厦]]只有一名特朗普支持者示威<ref>{{Cite web|last=|first=|date=2021-01-20|title=At NY Capitol, a Lone Trump Supporter Protests|url=https://www.nbcnewyork.com/news/politics/at-ny-capitol-a-lone-trump-supporter-protests/2840361/|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121112924/https://www.nbcnewyork.com/news/politics/at-ny-capitol-a-lone-trump-supporter-protests/2840361/|archive-date=2021-01-21|access-date=2021-01-20|website=NBC New York}}</ref>。1月17日，密歇根州[[布加洛運動|布加洛運動]]的部分成员在[[密西根州議會大廈|密西根州議會大廈]]外携带武器抗议，但未爆发暴力冲突<ref>{{Cite web|last=Wisely|first=John|date=2021-01-17|title=Lansing protest over the presidential election proves to be a dud|url=https://www.freep.com/story/news/local/michigan/2021/01/17/lansing-capitol-protest-presidential-election/4199510001/|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119213212/https://www.freep.com/story/news/local/michigan/2021/01/17/lansing-capitol-protest-presidential-election/4199510001/|archive-date=2021-01-19|access-date=2021-01-21|website=Detroit Free Press}}</ref>。全国公共广播电台认为暴力示威活动的疲弱有多方面原因，包括[[美国司法部|美国司法部]]追踪国会衝擊示威者警告执法部门策划“假旗”活动“围猎示威者”及和[[极端主义|极端主义]]和[[小党|小党]]运动有关的社交媒体账号、群组、页面及[[Parler|Parler]]等应用被封禁或下架<ref>{{Cite web|last=Chappell|first=Bill|last2=Allam|first2=Hannah|date=2021-01-20|title=No Large Protests In D.C. As President Biden Is Inaugurated|url=https://www.npr.org/sections/inauguration-day-live-updates/2021/01/20/958739876/no-large-protests-in-d-c-on-morning-of-bidens-inauguration|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120170412/https://www.npr.org/sections/inauguration-day-live-updates/2021/01/20/958739876/no-large-protests-in-d-c-on-morning-of-bidens-inauguration|archive-date=2021-01-20|access-date=2021-01-21|website=NPR}}</ref>。

== 收视率 ==
拜登的就职演说吸引各有线新闻频道及电视台共近4000万人收看<ref name=":35">{{Cite news|last=Koblin|first=John|date=2020-01-21|title=Biden’s Inauguration Scores Bigger TV Ratings Than Trump’s|work=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/01/21/business/media/biden-inauguration-tv-ratings-cnn.html|dead-url=no|access-date=2020-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122014805/https://www.nytimes.com/2021/01/21/business/media/biden-inauguration-tv-ratings-cnn.html|archive-date=2021-01-22|issn=0362-4331}}</ref>，黄金时段特别节目《庆祝美国》有2100多万观众收看<ref name=":35" />。与上述电视台2017年特朗普就职演说3830万名观众的收视率相比较，收视人数同比上涨4%<ref>{{Cite web|last=Lahut|first=Jake|date=2021-01-21|title=Over 1 million more people watched Biden's inauguration than Trump's|url=https://www.businessinsider.com/biden-inauguration-one-million-more-viewers-than-trump-tv-ratings-2021-1|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122023958/https://www.businessinsider.com/biden-inauguration-one-million-more-viewers-than-trump-tv-ratings-2021-1|archive-date=2021-01-22|access-date=2021-01-22|website=Business Insider}}</ref>，其中[[有线电视新闻网|有线电视新闻网]]领跑当天全台的收视率。与2017年相比，[[福斯新闻频道|福斯新闻频道]]收视率下跌77%，有线电视新闻网增长三倍，[[MSNBC|MSNBC]]增长四倍<ref name=":36">{{Cite web|last=Lahut|first=Jake|date=2021-01-21|title=Over 1 million more people watched Biden's inauguration than Trump's|url=https://www.businessinsider.com/biden-inauguration-one-million-more-viewers-than-trump-tv-ratings-2021-1|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122023958/https://www.businessinsider.com/biden-inauguration-one-million-more-viewers-than-trump-tv-ratings-2021-1|archive-date=2021-01-22|access-date=2021-01-22|website=Business Insider}}</ref>。

